age 5 | access-date = 2013-04-20 | archive-date = 2019-06-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190610170014/http://au.gamespy.com/articles/117/1176255p5.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]的游戏展示奖<ref>{{En icon}}{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/eurogamers-best-of-e3-2011 | title = Eurogamer's Best of E3 2011 | access-date = 2013-04-20 | archive-date = 2020-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201024205647/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/eurogamers-best-of-e3-2011 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。据官方网站所记，《生化奇兵：无限》在E3 2011期间赢得了超过85项奖项。<ref>{{En icon}}{{cite web | url = http://www.bioshockinfinite.com/the-game/ | title = The Game - ''BioShock Infinite'' | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130330040712/http://www.bioshockinfinite.com/the-game | archivedate = 2013年3月30日 | df =  }}</ref>

=== 正式版 ===
《生化奇兵：无限》一经发布就收到了普遍好评，评论指出游戏的剧情和视觉效果表现杰出。也有人将它和[[生化奇兵|生化奇兵]]第一作相媲美，一些评论家认为无限超越了前作。评论网站[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]给PS3版《生化奇兵：无限》的平均评分为95.94%<ref name="GRPS3" />，PC版为93.21%<ref name="GRPC" />，Xbox 360版为91.72%<ref name="GRX360" />。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]给游戏的PS3版95/100的分数<ref name="MCPS3" />，PC版95/100<ref name="MCPC" />，Xbox 360版93/100<ref name="MCX360" />，所有三个平台版本的游戏被认为“普遍好评”。

